engine/.pytest_tmp*/

# Generated run output (containment finding F5): a relative sealed output root or a repository-root
# dispatch lands the trainer's run tree + adapter here. Anchored to the repo root ONLY so a legitimate
# tracked artifact (e.g. examples/wbg/adapter-seq1536-baseline/adapter_model.safetensors) is never
# hidden. Runtime models/adapters/checkpoints belong outside the source tree; these rules stop an
# accidental in-checkout write from ever entering a tracked area.
/output/
/engine/output/
